  • Deprecated Enums 
    Enum and Description
    com.google.api.client.http.HttpMethod
    (scheduled to be removed in 1.13) Use HttpMethods instead. The purpose of this deprecation is to allow any arbitrary HTTP method to be used, rather than restrict it to a small set of HTTP methods.
